            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Transfer the <strong>courgette boats</strong> to a baking tray (or two!) and fill them with the <strong>Greek stuffing</strong></p><p>Add a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and put the tray[s] in the oven for 12-15 min or until the courgette has softened and the Greek cheese stuffing is golden – this is your<strong> Greek cheese-stuffed courgette</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1665560560047-x200.jpg",
