            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>ground turmeric</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> to the<strong> pestle & mortar</strong> and grind to a fine crumb – this is your <strong>pistachio dukkah</strong></p><p>Tip: Don't have a pestle & mortar? Pulse in a food processor instead!</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1665560566826-x200.jpg",
